er=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2007-12-13 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425072211/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2007/12/U-S-Under-23-MNT-Draws-With-China-In-First-Match-Of-Preparation-For-CONCACAF-Olympic-Qualifuing.aspx |archivedate=2012-04-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=zh-hans |url=http://teamchina.sports.sohu.com/20071213/n254076959.shtml |title=热身赛-朱挺错失两次绝杀良机 国奥0-0战平美国 |publisher=''teamchina.sports.sohu.com'' |date=20087-12-13 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305023016/http://teamchina.sports.sohu.com/20071213/n254076959.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>；次仗在[[廣州|廣州]][[越秀山体育场|越秀山体育场]]賀頓交出一個助攻協助球隊上半場領先3-0，下半場退下火線，完場前中國憑[[杜震宇|杜震宇]]的[[十二碼|十二碼]]扳平3-3<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2007/12/U-S-U-23-MNT-Draws-With-China-For-Second-Time-To-Close-Out-Tour-Of-Olympic-Host-Country.aspx |title=U.S. U-23 MNT Draws with China for Second Time to Close Out Tour of Olympic Host Country |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2007-12-16 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425072220/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2007/12/U-S-U-23-MNT-Draws-With-China-For-Second-Time-To-Close-Out-Tour-Of-Olympic-Host-Country.aspx |archivedate=2012-04-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=zh-hans |url=http://teamchina.sports.sohu.com/20071216/n254115457.shtml |title=热身赛-杜震宇独中两元 国奥3-3美国险演大逆转 |publisher=''teamchina.sports.sohu.com'' |date=20087-12-16 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304232840/http://teamchina.sports.sohu.com/20071216/n254115457.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2008年2月再獲召加入24人訓練營備戰[[2008年夏季奧運會男子足球比賽外圍賽_(中北美洲及加勒比海區)|京奧足球外圍賽]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/02/Nowak-Calls-24-Players-Into-Under-23-MNT-Training-Camp-Leading-Up-To-Olympic-Qualifying.aspx |title=Nowak Calls 24 Players Into Under-23 MNT Training Camp Leading Up to Olympic Qualifying |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-02-26 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425025857/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/02/Nowak-Calls-24-Players-Into-Under-23-MNT-Training-Camp-Leading-Up-To-Olympic-Qualifying.aspx |archivedate=2012-04-25 }}</ref></small>，並獲挑選進入參賽名單<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/03/Nowak-Names-20-Player-Roster-For-CONCACAF-Olympic-Qualifying-Campaign.aspx |title=Nowak Names 20-Player Roster for CONCACAF Olympic Qualifying Campaign |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-03-09 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425163429/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/03/Nowak-Names-20-Player-Roster-For-CONCACAF-Olympic-Qualifying-Campaign.aspx |archivedate=2012-04-25 }}</ref></small>。美國國奧隊在外圍賽準決賽以3-0擊敗加拿大後獲得[[2008年夏季奧林匹克運動會足球比賽|京奧足球項目]]參賽資格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/03/U-S-Under-23-MNT-Earns-Berth-To-2008-Olympic-Games-In-Beijing-Winning-Semifinal-Match-Against-Canada.aspx |title=U.S. Under-23 MNT Earns Berth to 2008 Olympic Games in Beijing, Winning Semifinal Match Against Canada, 3-0 |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-03-20 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110120056/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/03/U-S-Under-23-MNT-Earns-Berth-To-2008-Olympic-Games-In-Beijing-Winning-Semifinal-Match-Against-Canada.aspx |archivedate=2012-01-10 }}</ref></small>，但在決賽於[[加時賽|加時]]後0-1不敵洪都拉斯<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/03/U-S-Under-23-MNT-Fall-To-Honduras-In-Overtime-In-CONCACAF-Olympic-Qualifying-Final.aspx |title=U.S. Under-23 MNT Fall to Honduras in Overtime in CONCACAF Olympic Qualifying Final |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-03-23 |accessdate=201