23-MNT/2008/08/U-S-Men-Fall-To-Cameroon-1-0-In-Final-Tune-Up-Match-Before-The-Olympic-Games.aspx |archivedate=2009-12-16 }}</ref></small>。8月7日京奧足球項目分組首輪-{比}-賽，美國國奧隊在[[天津奧林匹克中心體育場|天津奧林匹克中心體育場]]對日本，賀頓於下半場47分鐘一箭定江山，協助球隊1-0旗開得勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.fifa.com/mensolympic/matches/round=250016/match=300051795/summary.html |title=Holden hits US past Japan |publisher=[[FIFA|''fifa.com'']] |date=2008-08-07 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |archive-date=2018-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929114650/https://www.fifa.com/mensolympic/matches/round=250016/match=300051795/summary.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/08/U-S-Earns-Three-Points-In-Olympic-Opener-With-1-0-Win-Against-Japan-In-Tianjin.aspx |title=U.S. Earns Three Points in Olympic Opener With 1-0 Win Against Japan in Tianjin |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-08-07 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091217095153/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/08/U-S-Earns-Three-Points-In-Olympic-Opener-With-1-0-Win-Against-Japan-In-Tianjin.aspx |archivedate=2009-12-17 }}</ref></small>。次仗賀頓繼續正選上陣，擔任左中場，美國於完場被荷蘭扳平2-2<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/08/U-S-Ties-Netherlands-2-2-Forcing-Pivotal-Match-Wednesday-Against-Nigeria.aspx |title=U.S. Ties Netherlands 2-2 Forcing Pivotal Match Wednesday Against Nigeria |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-08-10 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110427193010/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/08/U-S-Ties-Netherlands-2-2-Forcing-Pivotal-Match-Wednesday-Against-Nigeria.aspx |archivedate=2011-04-27 }}</ref></small>。分組賽最後一場移師[[北京工人體育場|北京工人體育場]]對尼日利亞，美國於開賽後僅3分鐘即有[[迈克尔·奥罗斯科|奥罗斯科]]（Michael Orozco）因畜意打肘被球證直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場，最終1-2落敗，排小組第三位未能出線<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/08/Down-To-10-Men-After-Three-Minutes-Valiant-U-S-Effort-Falls-Short-As-2-1-Loss-To-Nigeria-Knocks-Them.aspx |title=Down to 10 Men After Three Minutes, Valiant U.S. Effort Falls Short as 2-1 Loss to Nigeria Knocks Them Out of 2008 Olympics |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2008-08-13 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090815153250/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/U-23-MNT/2008/08/Down-To-10-Men-After-Three-Minutes-Valiant-U-S-Effort-Falls-Short-As-2-1-Loss-To-Nigeria-Knocks-Them.aspx |archivedate=2009-08-15 }}</ref></small>。

====國家隊====
由於大部分[[美國國家足球隊|國家隊]]主力球員在參賽[[2009年洲際國家盃|洲際國家盃]]後獲准休戰，賀頓得以在2009年6月24日獲國家隊挑選加入[[2009年美洲金盃|2009年美洲金盃]]參賽名單<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/06/U-S-Announces-Roster-For-2009-CONCACAF-Gold-Cup.aspx |title=U.S. Announces Roster for 2009 CONCACAF Gold Cup |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2009-06-24 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120425062455/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/06/U-S-Announces-Roster-For-2009-CONCACAF-Gold-Cup.aspx |archivedate=2012-04-25 }}</ref></small>。7月4日首次代表大國腳在[[2009年美洲金盃#分組賽|分組賽]]出戰[[格林納達國家足球隊|格林納達]]，於31分鐘頭球頂入個人首個國家隊入球，協助球隊大勝4-0完場<small><ref>{{cite news|language=en |url=http://concacaf.globalsportsmedia.com/page.php?sport=soccer&language_id=us&page=tournament&view=match&match_id=769383 |title=GRENADA 0-4 UNITED STATES |publisher=''concacaf.globalsportsmedia.com'' |date=2009-07-04 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003120610/http://concacaf.globalsportsmedia.com/page.php?sport=soccer&language_id=us&page=tournament&view=match&match_id=769383 |archivedate=2012-10-03 }}</ref></small>；次仗對[[洪都拉斯國家足球隊|洪都拉斯]]沒有上陣，7月11日分組賽最後一場對[[海地國家足球隊|海地]]，賀頓再次正選上陣，於完場前受傷補時階段在離門24碼勁射破網，為球隊扳平2-2完場，而球隊首個入球亦是得他助攻，賽果除使美國以小組首名出線外，更延續國家隊在美洲金盃分組賽連續25場不敗及主場對賽美洲金盃球隊56場不敗的紀錄<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/07/U-S-Mens-National-Team-Advances-To-Quarterfinals-Of-2009-Gold-Cup-With-2-2-Draw-With-Haiti-In-Final.aspx |title=U.S. Men's National Team Advances to Quarterfinals of 2009 Gold Cup With 2-2 Draw With Haiti In Final Group B Match |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2009-07-11|accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113042144/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/07/U-S-Mens-National-Team-Advances-To-Quarterfinals-Of-2009-Gold-Cup-With-2-2-Draw-With-Haiti-In-Final.aspx |archivedate=2010-01-13 }}</ref></small>。賀頓在準決賽對[[洪都拉斯國家足球隊|洪都拉斯]]貢獻兩個助攻協助美國2-0獲勝晉級決賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/07/US-Mens-National-Team-Advances-to-CONCACAF-Gold-Cup-Final-with-2-0-Win-Against-Honduras-in-Chicago.aspx |title=U.S. Men's National Team Advances to CONCACAF Gold Cup Final with 2-0 Win Against Honduras in Chicago |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090812155831/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/07/US-Mens-National-Team-Advances-to-CONCACAF-Gold-Cup-Final-with-2-0-Win-Against-Honduras-in-Chicago.aspx |archivedate=2009-08-12 }}</ref></small>。不幸決賽以0-5大敗於[[墨西哥國家足球隊|墨西哥]]腳下<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/07/US-Finishes-Second-in-2009-CONCACAF-Gold-Cup-After-Falling-to-Mexico-at-Giants-Stadium.aspx |title=U.S. Finishes Second in 2009 CONCACAF Gold Cup After Falling to Mexico at Giants Stadium |publisher=''ussoccer.com'' |date=2009-07-26 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113041922/http://www.ussoccer.com/News/Mens-National-Team/2009/07/US-Finishes-Second-in-2009-CONCACAF-Gold-Cup-After-Falling-to-Mexico-at-Giants-Stadium.aspx |archivedate=2010-01-13 }}</ref></small>，但賀頓在賽事中的表現使他獲選入「賽事最佳陣容」（All-Tournament Team）<small><ref>{{Cite web |language=en |title=Dos Santos Chosen as Gold Cup MVP |url=http://www.goldcup.org/page/GoldCup/AwardsDetail/0,,12802~1734174,00.html |publisher=''GoldCup.org'' |date=2009-07-26 |accessdate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090731064333/http://www.goldcup.org/page/GoldCup/AwardsDetail/0%2C%2C12802~1734174%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-07-31 }}</ref></small>。

