==私人生活==
賀頓畢業於[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[休斯敦|休斯敦]]的雅迪國際學校（Awty International School），他自2006年成為[[美國|美國]][[公民|公民]]<small><ref name="longman">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/26/sports/soccer/26holden.html |title=Understudy Is Hitting His Marks for U.S. Team |work=[[纽约时报|''nytimes.com'']] |date=2009-07-26 |accessdate=2009-08-21 |archive-date=2018-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614123224/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/26/sports/soccer/26holden.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但仍持有[[英國|英國]][[護照|護照]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/1614/americans-abroad/2010/01/11/1737739/report-stuart-holden-set-for-bolton-trial |title=Report: Stuart Holden Set For Bolton Trial |work=''goal.com'' |date=2010-01-11 |accessdate=2010-01-28 |archive-date=2016-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414132320/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/1614/americans-abroad/2010/01/11/1737739/report-stuart-holden-set-for-bolton-trial |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他的父親患[[胰腺癌|胰腺癌]]6年後，於2009年2月去世<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://web.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20091209&content_id=7780924&vkey=news_hou&fext=.jsp&team=t200 |title=Holden honored for public service |publisher=[[美國職業足球大聯盟|''mlsnet.com'']] |date=2009-09-12 |accessdate=2010-01-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119071859/http://web.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20091209&content_id=7780924&vkey=news_hou&fext=.jsp&team=t200 |archivedate=2010-01-19 }}</ref></small>，其母親與妹妹仍然居於休斯敦<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://goal.com/en-us/news/1679/us-national-team/2009/09/23/1519545/holden-playing-for-the-us-a-no-brainer |title=Holden: Playing For The U.S. A No-Brainer |publisher=''goal.com'' |date=2009-09-23 |accessdate=2010-01-28 |archive-date=2018-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180714021826/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/1679/us-national-team/2009/09/23/1519545/holden-playing-for-the-us-a-no-brainer |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。賀頓最鍾愛的球隊是[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]，曾5次造訪[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]。

賀頓的弟弟[[尤安·霍尔登|尤安·霍尔登]]（Euan Holden）曾效力新墨西哥大學，司職左閘，在「2010年MLS超級選秀會」（2010 MLS SuperDraft）於第四輪第62選被[[休斯敦迪纳摩|休斯敦迪纳摩]]選中，但他沒有加盟休斯敦迪纳摩，追隨兄長的腳步，到[[歐洲|歐洲]]不同球會試訓，獲剛降班丹甲的[[Vejle_Boldklub|維積利]]（Vejle Boldklub）賞識提供一年合約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/1614/americans-abroad/2010/02/06/1779424/euan-holden-signs-one-year-deal-with-denmarks-vejle-bk |title=Euan Holden Signs One Year Deal With Denmark's Vejle BK |publisher=''goal.com'' |date=2010-02-06 |accessdate=2010-03-05 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308014726/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/1614/americans-abroad/2010/02/06/1779424/euan-holden-signs-one-year-deal-with-denmarks-vejle-bk |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===职业游戏生涯===
在成为职业足球运动员之前，霍尔登曾经是游戏[[反恐精英|反恐精英]]（CS）的职业玩家。他是美国CS职业战队Forsaken的创始人，之后又成为战队队长。他和战队一起获得2002年[[世界电子竞技大赛|世界电子竞技大赛]]（WCG2002）美国区预选赛亚军以及[[职业电子竞技联盟|CPL2003]]的第八名。之后霍尔登决定将自己的主要精力放在克莱姆森大学足球队，并退出Forsaken战队，结束自己的职业游戏生涯<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sk-gaming.com/content/29602-ExCS_player_makes_US_World_Cup_team |title=Ex-CS star Holden makes US World Cup team |access-date=2011-09-13 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108113732/https://www.sk-gaming.com/content/29602-ExCS_player_makes_US_World_Cup_team |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.mymym.com/en/news/18646.html Former Counter-strike player Stuart Holden] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602233629/http://www.mymym.com/en/news/18646.html |date=2010-06-02 }}</ref>。

